data.description: Huge pool!  Brand new kitchen!    Come check out this 4 bed 2 bath home in NW Palm Bay with an oversized pool.  Beautifully renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, updated backsplash and butcher block countertop.  Spacious living room with wood-burning fireplace.  Separate  dining area and family room overlooking the pool.  Split floorplan.  Updated master bathroom with tiled walk-in shower.  Tankless water heater.  Roof is just a couple years old.  Fenced yard.  Come take a look today!
